    Activity

    Interface for conflict handling for the Activity Object
    ConflictException
    Constructor for the ConflictException error message.
    Course
    Extends Activities to add fields for course name, section, credit hours, and instructor ID associated with the class.
    CourseCatalog
    Maintains a catalog of all classes available for the student.
    CourseCatalogPanel
    Creates a user interface for working with the CourseCatalog.
    CourseNameValidator
    Finite state machine class which intent is to filter course names to confirm if they are of a valid format or not.
    CourseNameValidatorFSM
    Finite State Machine for checking whether a Course's Name is valid.
    CourseRecordIO
    Reads Course records from text files.
    CourseRoll
    List of students for a specific class.

    Constructor for the InvalidTransitionException error message.

    Custom application of the linked list storage system.
    LinkedQueue<E>
    A implementation of the Queue data structure onto the Linked node based list
    LinkedStack<E>
    A implementation of the Stack data structure onto the Linked node based list
    PackSchedulerGUI
    Main GUI for the PackScheduler project.
    Queue<E>
    Queue Interface to be used to help add methods for different data structures to Implement a waitlist capability.
    RegistrationManager
    Utility class for handling interactions between the User objects (student and registar) and the different directories (studentdirectory and course catalog), including user login activity
    Schedule
    Utility class to manage the students course schedule.
    Stack<E>
    Stack Interface to be used to help add methods for different data structures to implement a waitlist capability.
    Student
    A student object that contains the first name, last name, id, email address, password, and max number of credits they can take in a given semester.
    StudentDirectory
    Maintains a directory of all students enrolled at NC State.
    StudentDirectoryPanel
    Creates a user interface for working with the StudentDirectory.
    StudentRecordIO
    The general IO for the student aspect of NCSU Scheduler.
    StudentRegistrationPanel
    Creates a user interface for students to register for classes.
    User
    A user object that contains the first name, last name, id, email address, and password for a user.
